description:
Endless Runner (Yeah i know it's so creative) is my first Unity project. If you like or dislike this creative game, I would appreciate it if you give your feedback in the comments. It Will be on Google Play Store.

Controls;
<ul><li><strong>Space - Jump</strong></li><li><strong>Left Control (ctrl) - Crouch</strong></li><li><strong>ESC - Stop game</strong></li></ul>
